  <title translate="true">Inventory</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Inventory</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Inventory.prg is a small inventory form. A user can enter a barcode (by hand or by scanning if a keyboard scanner is attached) and specify a quantity. The num pad can be used to add digits to the quantity (mainly to fill the space on the form). Clicking on Save appends the current values to the inventory.txt text file and clears all text boxes.</text></para>
